OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,FThe UK's terror watchdog has
OL,7,Frecommended that a new offence to
OL,8,Fprevent mass casualty attacks before
OL,9,Fthey happen, should be considered in
OL,10,Flight of the Southport murders.
OL,12,FBut the review commission by the Home
OL,13,FSecretary following the attacks in
OL,14,FJuly, also concluded that the
OL,15,Fterrorism definition should not be
OL,16,Fchanged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
