OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,FJonathan Hall KC said the legal
OL,7,Fdefinition is "already wide" and
OL,8,Fexpanding the threshold would
OL,9,F"increase the possibility of
OL,10,Finaccurate use and, in theory, abuse".
OL,12,FHis review commissioned in January to
OL,13,Fexamine terror legislation "in light
OL,14,Fof modern threats we face" also warns
OL,15,Fthat extending terror liability could
OL,16,Fresult in "unacceptable restrictions
OL,17,Fon freedom of expression".
OL,19,FHe warned: "The risk of unintended
OL,20,Fconsequences through rushed reform is
OL,21,Fextremely high.
