OL,6,F"The Independent Reviewer of Terrorism
OL,7,FLegislation's findings come as Prime
OL,8,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer said Britain
OL,9,Ffaces a new threat from "extreme
OL,10,Fviolence carried out by loners,
OL,11,Fmisfits, young men in their bedrooms"
OL,12,Ffollowing the Southport murders.
OL,14,FSir Keir said the law and framework
OL,15,Ffor responding needed to be
OL,16,Fappropriate to the "new threat" and
OL,17,Fwhatever legal changes were necessary
OL,18,Fwould be made.
