OL,6,FAxel Rudakubana was jailed for a
OL,7,Fminimum of 52 years for the murders of
OL,8,Fthree girls and attempted murders of
OL,9,Feight other children, who cannot be
OL,10,Fnamed for legal reasons, class
OL,11,Finstructor Leanne Lucas and
OL,12,Fbusinessman John Hayes at a Taylor
OL,13,FSwift-themed dance class in July last
OL,14,Fyear.
