OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,FDespite contact with state agencies
OL,7,Fsuch as Prevent, aimed at countering
OL,8,Fterrorism, authorities failed to stop
OL,9,Fthe attack which claimed the lives of
OL,10,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, Bebe
OL,11,FKing, six, and Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,12,Fseven.
OL,14,FRudakubana's acts of extreme violence
OL,15,Fwere not considered terrorism under
OL,16,Fexisting laws because there was no
OL,17,Fevidence of his purpose being to
OL,18,Fadvance an ideological cause as set
OL,19,Fout in the terror definition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
