OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,FBut Mr Hall said: "Such is the
OL,7,Ffunctional importance of the terrorism
OL,8,Fdefinition, that redefinition would
OL,9,Falter the landscape.
OL,11,F"It would risk major false positives `
OL,12,Fthe prosecution of people who by no
OL,13,Fstretch of the imagination are
OL,14,Fterrorists ` and extend terrorism
OL,15,Fliability into novel terrain.
OL,17,F"People swapping violent war footage
OL,18,Fwould be at risk of encouraging
OL,19,Fterrorism, resulting in unacceptable
OL,20,Frestrictions on freedom of expression.
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
