OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,F"He added that the current "very wide"
OL,7,Fdefinition depends on the discretion
OL,8,Fof the police and authorities on
OL,9,Fdeciding who to arrest and prosecute.
OL,11,F"It has been my experience that this
OL,12,Fdiscretion has been exercised capably
OL,13,Fand well, so that individuals are not
OL,14,Fexposed to irrationality, heavy-
OL,15,Fhandedness or bias.
OL,17,F"But this is a product of a mature and
OL,18,Fdefined system operating with a
OL,19,Ffamiliar threshold.
