OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,FAltering the threshold would not only
OL,7,Fexpand the reach of terrorism
OL,8,Flegislation but would increase the
OL,9,Fpossibility of inaccurate use and, in
OL,10,Ftheory, abuse."
OL,12,FHe said for some cases it will be
OL,13,Fclear to investigators the attack was
OL,14,Ffor "purely personal motives" and
OL,15,Fsaying it is not treated as terrorism
OL,16,Fmakes "good sense to do so".
