OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,F"The key point to make is that
OL,7,Fterrorism legislation is not the UK's
OL,8,Fmain protection against this sort of
OL,9,Fattacker: what counts is gun control,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FHe added of school shootings and young
OL,13,Fcopycats that it is "foreseeable" that
OL,14,Fother types of violent attacks will
OL,15,Fstart a copycat craze, "most likely
OL,16,Famongst the cohort of isolated often
OL,17,Fbullied teenagers with poor mental
OL,18,Fhealth, neurodivergence or personality
OL,19,Fdisorder for whom grudges and
OL,20,Fgrievances become reasons for violence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]uD@UOUuD@aO]wD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
