OL,3,CNew terrorism offence recommended in
OL,4,Cwake of Southport attack
OL,6,F"Few will be terrorists applying the
OL,7,Fdefinition."
OL,9,FInstead, the watchdog recommended
OL,10,Fcreating an offence to prevent mass
OL,11,Fcasualty attacks before they happen,
OL,12,Fsimilar to terrorism offences applying
OL,13,Fto an offender preparing for an attack.
OL,15,F"It has become clear to me during the
OL,16,Fpreparation of this report during
OL,17,FJanuary and February 2025 that there
OL,18,Fis a real and not theoretical gap for
OL,19,Flone individuals who plan mass
OL,20,Fkillings," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
